204
00:31:08,397 --> 00:31:11,192
keď moja matka náhle zmizla.

205
00:31:22,829 --> 00:31:25,600
Vonia ako ty.

206
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:28,013
Prikrývka tiež vonia ako ty.

207
00:31:29,555 --> 00:31:31,421
Áno, synček môj...

208
00:31:33,013 --> 00:31:34,730
Ja spím.

209
00:31:34,730 --> 00:31:37,639
Naozaj? Tak spi.

210
00:31:58,714 --> 00:32:00,339
Mama?

211
00:32:10,770 --> 00:32:13,079
Mama!

212
00:32:13,726 --> 00:32:16,301
Mama!

